#

Grilled Teriyaki Salmon with Steamed Broccoli and Jasmine Rice

$15
550 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

FishSoy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

EasyHealthyQuick

Description

A delightful blend of sweet and savory teriyaki flavors paired with tender salmon, fresh broccoli, and aromatic jasmine rice.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillet: 2 (6 oz)
  • Teriyaki sauce: 1/4 cup
  • Broccoli florets: 2 cups
  • Jasmine rice: 1 cup
  • Water: 2 cups
  • Olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • Sesame seeds (optional): 1 tablespoon
